parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn, leading to loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The power steering warning light appears on the dashboard
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle is hard to maneuver
the power steering system malfunctions
and other safety features such as lane departure warning
blind spot detection
and forward collision warning may also fail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in receiving parts for recall repairs can leave vehicles with safety defects on the road, putting drivers and passengers at risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Owners receive notification of a recall
but the parts to repair the defect are not available
and the dealer is unable to perform the repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the vehicle stalls
the battery charging and check engine warning lights are illuminated
the "Performance Limited" "Service Fuel System" and "Service Charging System" messages are displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The software update can cause the vehicle's electrical system to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system fails
the vehicle's systems malfunction
the vehicle's sensors are affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the autonomous emergency braking system can cause the vehicle to suddenly brake, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly brakes
the vehicle makes an emergency beeping sound
the vehicle's brakes are applied unnecessarily.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the start/stop system can cause the vehicle to shift into park unexpectedly, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts into park unexpectedly
the vehicle's systems malfunction
the "Service Start/Stop System" message is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the rear camera component can cause the vehicle's rear camera system to fail, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The rear camera system fails
the radio does not project an image when the vehicle is in reverse
the "Rear Camera Component Fault" message is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Blinker and Side View Camera Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the blinker and side view camera systems can cause the vehicle's systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The blinker system malfunctions
the side view camera system malfunctions
the vehicle's systems are affected.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring harness can cause the vehicle's electrical system to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system fails
the vehicle's systems malfunction
the wiring harness is damaged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, hesitate, or fail to accelerate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Vehicle fails to accelerate
hesitates upon depression of the accelerator pedal
transmission fails to shift into higher gear
engine over-revs
vehicle goes into "limp-home" mode
gear-shifting noises
and shudder.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Hybrid powertrain malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose electric mode or electric assist, leading to reduced performance and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Vehicle goes into "Fuel/Oil Refresh Mode" (FORM)
depriving the vehicle of electric mode or electric assist
"limp-home" mode
transmission failure to shift into higher gear
engine over-revving.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Valve Train Noise and Performance Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine valve train noise and performance issues can cause the engine to misfire, vibrate, and lose power, leading to reduced performance and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Valve train noise that worsens as the engine gets hotter
engine misfiring
oil temperature remains high
oil pressure at idling speed is low
engine stalls
service engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal knocking sound can cause the driver to lose confidence in the vehicle's braking system, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Knocking sound when depressing the brake pedal
sound ceases when shifting to park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ADAS malfunction can cause the vehicle to suddenly accelerate or decelerate, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Vehicle suddenly speeds up or slows down when approaching stopped traffic
despite the ADAS system being active.
